    "Note that the theoretical positions of the FOVs, defined by the microscope, were used as initial positions for stitching.",
    "Cell boundaries were segmented with Cellpose (v2.1.1) 88, 89.",
    "The \"cyto\" model in Cellpose was fine tuned on each tissue by manually segmenting a handful of composite images of DRAQ5 (nuclei channel) and N9 cDNA stain (cyto channel) using the package's graphical user interface.",
